data.title: Pat's Hot Tubs & Pools
data.text:
Pat's Hot Tubs and Pools carries a full line of pool and hot tub chemicals, parts, equipment, accessories and maintenance supplies. We use quality products to provide the ultimate pool and hot tub experience while keeping your maintenance simple & safe so you have more time for FUN! If we don't carry it, you can bring in the part you need or a picture of it and we will try to find it for you.

Skimmers Skimmer Baskets Hot Tub Filters vacuum plates Gaskets O-Rings

Filter Lids In Line Chlorinators New Pool Pumps New Pool Filters Spare Jets Flex PVC

Pool Plumbing Pieces Floating Chlorinators Skimmer Nets Pool Poles Pool Vacuums

Thermometers Pool Patches Hot Tub Cover Locks Hot Tub Pillows Hot Tub Steps

Custom Hot Tub Covers ~If your hot tub/spa is installed outdoors making sure your cover is in top condition will be extremely important. The replacement cover you choose for your hot tub will determine whether your electricity bill will skyrocket or remain reasonably consistent over the years. In time, you may regret not having chosen the best possible cover to ensure you save on energy costs. Contact us today and we can get a new cover for you in your choice of colors.
